Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 總是說超啊超的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快成達茲納大叔的口頭禪了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來變得超可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然看起來很可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對拍馬屁還真是沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不害臊的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是超認真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人哥哥在我們國家可是英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說如此哦 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去總是自以為是 到處惹事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七班那時真的很開心啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎 那位大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要復仇的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茲卡德大叔 真讓人懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張 惹出不少事來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在此碰見 就說明你的末日到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族的不共戴天之敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡塔茲 痛快地一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙都想把我生吞活剝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得相當可愛不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 誰讓你猜拳輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧鴕鳥一職就非你莫屬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆意外地般配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪裡般配了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從走失的貓到走失的狗 再到走失的豬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於輪到走失的鴕鳥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體型變大倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但儘是這些無聊的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力根本無法提升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:04:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂任務 並不是用來提升忍者的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和修行可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解你急切的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用鴕鳥做對手 來提升你的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢 快點開始吧 你不是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡找家旅館休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥先生也該累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只有我們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日落之前就能回村了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊怎麼了 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連你們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…像是在復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇…有人要報仇雪恨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光天化日之下 聚眾血拼沒問題嗎 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇許可書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據某些國家規定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當某人被殺害後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可其遺族進行復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果持有該國所發的許可證書
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在其他國家也能進行復仇行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是那位茲卡德大叔的遠房親戚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜被那個仇家叫了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了 在背後用大石頭暗算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殘忍地殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追殺仇人 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔被族人推選了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個大壞蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金蚊老大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人在復仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來蠻有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得哪方會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說得好…狼總比兔子跑得快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未必哦 仇敵一方似乎胸有成竹 面不改色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可報不了仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混賬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差那麼一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門外漢給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是有過34回復仇經驗的專家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那豈不是失敗34回了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不現實…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我都要復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要替族人鹿藏大叔報仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從背後偷襲的卑鄙行為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果此仇無法昭雪的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話對我太過殘忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不試試又怎麼能知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次或許就能成功復仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會運用全部的忍者技能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫大叔成為一代復仇宗師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在逞能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就暫時交給鳴人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先回旅館休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 安心交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的復仇憤怒指標不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應當無論何時都能瞬間爆發出怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣面對突如其來的復仇 就不會手忙腳亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆 很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來背你這混蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋要去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去那旁邊的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很近啊 混蛋 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再遠點也沒關係啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得有點…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是丁點的仇恨 也不能輕易放過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓復仇融入生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞肩之恨 撞肩之仇 撞肩之怨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中要充滿了對敵人的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而將那股怨恨淋漓盡致地發洩於手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 被憎恨的仇家怎麼會如此清秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔果然不適合當復仇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不適合當教官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何如此執著於復仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我無臉返回家鄉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想盡快了結此事 然後回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到年邁的父母的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥發瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏身手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還呆著幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥咬斷了繩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然身手不凡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔明明那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼始終不能復仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當看到那傢伙的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量就逐漸消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神…那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔在那之後怎樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計為了復仇 再度啟程了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會永遠持續下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 想報仇的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被你的真誠所打動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你完成復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把這傢伙帶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請毫無顧忌地來場復仇之戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場決鬥要讓我們金蚊一家來組織
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場決鬥到底誰是最後的贏家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下注吧 下注吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪一邊比較強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是仇家更厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大叔太無能了 毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我賭仇家500兩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那賭金少的一方就算我金蚊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那大叔使出真本領的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我大賺一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然利用大叔的復仇來賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切到此為此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意 我不會輕易被你殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 不看對方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣或許會贏 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說鳴人的指導奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得…總覺得這場決鬥讓人很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正像大叔所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的臉…眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要流露出那樣的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可能被我殺掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不打算傷害大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都無法對他下手的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔現在應該心知肚明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 刀刃是鈍的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是不會殺人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個雙胞胎弟弟 名叫影木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙胞胎弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影木曾借錢給你族的鹿藏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因生了孩子急需用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便前去催促還錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而鹿藏卻裝傻 矢口否認借錢一事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果兩人起了爭執 一起倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而鹿藏倒地時 碰到了曬乾貨的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說這是意外事故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影木打算去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從證據來看 他毫無疑問是個殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定代替他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為了弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而弟弟則同他的妻子以及剛出生的孩子隱姓埋名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我則故意暴露身份 吸引追殺者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓那樣的好人糟蹋了人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個惡人 給社會 家人 朋友添盡了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此來贖罪 再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切都是我弟弟的片面之詞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有真憑實據
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信由你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信的話 就殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就姑且信你一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對復仇有些厭倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 你都裝作有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就由我來裝作復仇好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 你都要報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 你們可就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…來拔刀相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓我想要早些回村子裡修行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來參合一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了吧 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他倆決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇還真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不得不報之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我還太幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡卡西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為木葉發生了大事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要馬上趕來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想跟他聊聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事…事實上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助他…這個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助呢 因為跟我吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以離開了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 很快就會把他給帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他回來後再跟他打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時佐助也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 因為三角關係鬧出糾紛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在到底在哪裡啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有父母兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就孤身一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為有羈絆才會感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失去羈絆又將如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在能夠瞭解了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂復仇到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解一些痛楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有承受過相同的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法真正的理解他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以為自己很瞭解佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可實際上我根本不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 無論我在終結之谷對佐助說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都無動於衷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不瞭解佐助的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能跟他一同歡笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連跟他打架的資格都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之後我想跟他好好地打一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會讓佐助回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七班的所有人也能一起歡笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯合地點的確就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我們先到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的協作任務竟然遲到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂隱真的有意向木葉修好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:23:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到了 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到和這傢伙合作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅 羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同盟國的夥伴們 大家要好好相處啊
